#### About

Divine Voxel Engine Foundation is one of the libraries that compose Divine Voxel Engine. It is a library for voxel scenes and games where the assumed size of the voxels are 1 meter cubes. 
Beyond that though it makes full use of web workers and SharedArrayBuffers to generate, load, and update the world in parallel. 

The library is renderer independent meaning it just generates raw mesh data that can be used by a renderer. The scope of libraries for Divine Voxel Engine includes a Babylon.Js, Three.Js and React Three Fiber renderer. 


